Definition for "åŠåˆ†å¿ƒ" is when the user is adjusting computer settings, playing background music, using productivity tools, reading and replying to emails, responding to instant messages, etc.
Definition for "åˆ†å¿ƒä¸­" is most of the screen current activity deviate from Work Goal: "${workContext}" 

Possible values for the "status" field are ONLY: "ä¸“æ³¨ä¸­", "åŠåˆ†å¿ƒ", "åˆ†å¿ƒä¸­".
The "reason" field should be a brief explanation (under 50 characters) in Chinese.`;

  try {
    // For vision analysis, we need to use a vision-capable model
    const visionPayload = {
